  "original_title": "22 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd: \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Changes are necessary in 22: Sri Lanka Bar Association",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The 22nd Amendment Act proposed by the government has made some changes in its ideas. Saliya Peiris, President of the Sri Lankan Bar Association, has said that the country's economic and political stability can only be created if such amendments are carried forward.",
        "The government should have made a few changes in the ideas of the 22nd Amendment Act which it has now proposed. Economic and political stability of the country can be created only if such reforms are carried forward. The lack of independence of government institutions is one of the reasons for the country's economic crisis.",
        "If the Constituent Assembly is not independent, the independence of the nominations made and accepted by the Constituent Assembly will be questioned. So even though the 22nd Amendment includes the Constituent Assembly and the Independent Commissions, they do not become meaningfully independent institutions.",
        "The 22nd Amendment states that the President can hold the Ministry of Defence. But the institutions and areas under the Ministry of Defense are not limited.",
        "So even if the 22nd amendment is brought in, the President can gazette and establish different agencies under his Ministry of Defence. What the new constitution seeks through the amendment is to limit the executive powers of the president. But in 22nd the powers will not be limited and the objective is to provide officers, he said."
      ],
